album.title: So Fresh - The Hits of Summer 2008 & The Hits of 2007

wiki.content:
"It's Not Over" is the first official single from Daughtry's first album, Daughtry. The song was used as a teaser to the second season fall finale of Prison Break. It was certified Platinum in April 2007. As of August 2007 it was in the top ten digital selling songs of the year.
